  "english": "<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">So my buddy Marcus just got promoted to senior director at his company, and honestly, nobody&#x27;s surprised. That guy has been <strong>grinding it out</strong> for years — late nights, weekend calls, the whole nine yards. I remember back in 2022, he was stuck in a dead-end role and was seriously thinking about throwing in the towel. He came to me one night and said, &quot;Dude, I don&#x27;t know if I&#x27;m cut out for this corporate stuff.&quot; I told him straight up, &quot;Bro, you didn&#x27;t come this far just to come this far. <strong>Keep your eye on the prize</strong>.&quot;</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">And he did. He started <strong>going the extra mile</strong> — volunteering for cross-functional projects, building relationships with leadership, basically making himself impossible to ignore. A lot of people at his office were just <strong>phoning it in</strong>, doing the bare minimum, but Marcus? He was out there <strong>moving the needle</strong> every single quarter. His boss even told him he was on the <strong>fast track</strong> to upper management.</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">Of course, it wasn&#x27;t all smooth sailing. He got passed over for a promotion last year, which was a real gut punch. Some people would&#x27;ve <strong>thrown in the towel</strong> right then and there, but Marcus is the kind of guy who <strong>rolls with the punches</strong>. He took the feedback, leveled up his leadership skills, and came back stronger. He told me, &quot;I&#x27;m not gonna let one &#x27;no&#x27; define my whole career. I&#x27;m <strong>in it for the long haul</strong>.&quot;</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">Now he&#x27;s basically <strong>calling the shots</strong> in his department, and he just <strong>landed</strong> a huge client that everyone else thought was a lost cause. The dude literally went from thinking about quitting to running the show. If that doesn&#x27;t prove that <strong>the grind pays off</strong>, I don&#x27;t know what does. Super proud of him.</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">我哥们儿Marcus刚升了他公司的高级总监，说实话，没人觉得意外。这哥们儿这些年一直在<strong>拼命干</strong>（grinding it out）——加班到深夜、周末接电话，什么苦都吃过。我记得2022年的时候，他困在一个没前途的岗位上，一度认真考虑过<strong>放弃</strong>（throwing in the towel）。有天晚上他跟我说：&quot;兄弟，我不知道自己是不是干公司这块的料。&quot;我直接跟他说：&quot;哥们，你走了这么远不是为了到此为止。<strong>盯紧目标，别分心</strong>（Keep your eye on the prize）。&quot;</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">他真的做到了。他开始<strong>付出额外的努力</strong>（going the extra mile）——主动参加跨部门项目、跟管理层搞好关系，基本上让自己变成一个不可忽视的存在。他公司很多人都在<strong>敷衍了事、混日子</strong>（phoning it in），只做最低限度的工作，但Marcus呢？他每个季度都在<strong>推动实质性进展</strong>（moving the needle）。他老板甚至跟他说，他已经走上了晋升高管的<strong>快车道</strong>（fast track）。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">当然，也不是一帆风顺的。去年他被跳过了一次晋升机会，那真的是一记重击。换作别人可能当场就<strong>放弃</strong>（thrown in the towel）了，但Marcus这人就是能<strong>随机应变、扛住打击</strong>（rolls with the punches）。他接受了反馈，提升了领导力，然后更强地杀了回来。他跟我说：&quot;我不会让一个&#x27;不行&#x27;定义我整个职业生涯。我是<strong>打持久战的</strong>（in it for the long haul）。&quot;</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">现在他基本上在部门里<strong>说了算</strong>（calling the shots），而且刚刚<strong>拿下了</strong>（landed）一个所有人都觉得没戏的大客户。这哥们儿真的从想辞职变成了掌管全局。如果这都不能证明<strong>努力终有回报</strong>（the grind pays off），那我不知道还有什么能证明了。真心为他骄傲。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\">**grind it out**</strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 咬牙坚持、拼命干（强调长期辛苦的努力）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全美通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 职场闲聊、励志对话、社交媒体</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\">**keep your eye on the prize**</strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 盯紧目标、别分心</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全美通用（源自民权运动歌曲）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 朋友鼓励、职场激励、教练训话</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\">**going the extra mile**</strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 付出额外的努力，做超出本分的事</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全美通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 职场评价、日常鼓励、绩效面谈</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-